While I was talking to Lisa, I had become mentally tired. [p]
But I did find myself faintly attracted to her.[p]
An unexplainable irritableness took control of my feelings.[p]
I placed my hands on one of the two heaters lined up under the reception counter, [p]
and then was gripped with a strange sensation.[p]


